# Architectural guidance is distributed via DevTeamSwarm.app (or a developer's
# local DevTeamSwarmControl checkout). It is proprietary and must not land in
# this public repo. `bin/sync-guidance.sh` populates `src/guidance/` at
# install time from whichever source is available; if none is, the MCP server
# runs without architectural-intent injection (a graceful, degraded mode).
src/guidance/*
!src/guidance/.keep
!src/guidance/README.md
